---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Retire Right Radio Blog | Capital Wealth Advisors"
description: "Expert retirement planning insights from Mike Stevens and the Capital Wealth Advisors team. Based on Retire Right Radio episodes aired on KAOX, KID, KNRS, and KSL."
permalink: /blog/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { name: "Blog", url: "/blog/" }
---

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   HERO
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="titan-page-hero">
    <div class="titan-page-hero-inner">
        <p class="titan-section-label">RETIRE RIGHT RADIO</p>
        <h1 class="titan-page-hero-h1">Expert Retirement Planning Insights</h1>
        <p class="titan-page-hero-sub">In-depth articles from Mike Stevens and the Capital Wealth team, based on episodes aired on KAOX, KID, KNRS, and KSL.</p>
    </div>
</section>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   BLOG GRID — Titan card style (matches /guides/)
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="guides-hub">
    <div class="guides-hub-inner">
        <div class="guides-grid">
            {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="guide-card">
                {% set topicTags = [] %}
                {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                    {% if tag != 'blog' %}
                        {% set topicTags = (topicTags.push(tag), topicTags) %}
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                {% if topicTags.length %}
                <span class="guide-card-label">{{ topicTags[0] | upper }}</span>
                {% endif %}
                <h3 class="guide-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                <p class="guide-card-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                <div class="guide-card-meta">
                    <span>{{ post.data.date | date }}</span>
                    {% if post.data.readTime %}<span>{{ post.data.readTime }} min read</span>{% endif %}
                </div>
                <span class="guide-card-link">Read Article →</span>
            </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   CTA — Titan service-process style
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="service-process">
    <div class="service-process-inner">
        <div class="service-process-left">
            <h2 class="service-process-h2">Hear Something That Resonated?</h2>
            <p class="service-process-subtitle">These articles are the starting point. Your personalized plan is the destination.</p>
            <a href="/contact/" class="service-process-cta">SCHEDULE CONSULTATION</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-process-right">
            <div class="service-process-steps">
                <div class="service-process-step">
                    <div class="service-process-step-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">
                        <span class="service-process-step-title">Step 1) Free Consultation</span>
                        <span class="service-process-chevron">▾</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-process-step-body">
                        <p>30 minutes with Mike Stevens to review your situation. No cost. No pressure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-process-step">
                    <div class="service-process-step-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">
                        <span class="service-process-step-title">Step 2) Comprehensive Analysis</span>
                        <span class="service-process-chevron">▾</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-process-step-body">
                        <p>We model your income, taxes, healthcare, and estate plan with real numbers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-process-step">
                    <div class="service-process-step-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('active')">
                        <span class="service-process-step-title">Step 3) Your Retirement Money Map</span>
                        <span class="service-process-chevron">▾</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-process-step-body">
                        <p>A clear, coordinated plan that turns savings into reliable retirement income.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>